data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home that has been thoughtfully updated with new appliances, fresh carpet and a vibrant coat of paint. As you enter, you're greeted by an open and bright living space with ample natural light streaming through the newly installed windows. The cozy kitchen, though compact, is efficiently designed with modern appliances. Outside, the front yard is impeccably well-maintained, offering beautiful curb appeal, making this home a perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality, ready to create lasting memories. This house is ready to be called Home, contact us for a private showing and to see what your options are for help with closing costs!
